summary: Can there just be an agreement among the critters going to the live show that anything you post about it not be in the critical...
body: Can there just be an agreement among the critters going to the live show that anything you post about it not be in the critical role tag. It’s all very well and good to say ‘blacklist this tag’ but everyone has a different tag that they’re posting under making it very hard to blacklist them all. I love scrolling through the critical role tag to find art and meta and theories and all that jazz so I would appreciate no one posting in there about search for grog until the vod is available for us all
